		  <td class="forum_boardrow1" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 1px;" valign="top"><div id="message30031145">Genres are vague in general, so SoL isn't unique in that sense. <br />
<br />
It might also be more accurate to call the genre 'Slice of Daily Life' because every anime that features characters shows their lives—but, of course, that's not what SoL refers to. To me, SoL implies, at the very least, a relatively unchanging state of normalcy and complete non-emergency.</div><div class="postActions"></div></td>
