<br />
But Aria's setting is firmly sci-fi and so much of the show (particularly The Natural) is focused around this setting; couldn't it be considered sci-fi, perhaps even predominately so? It even has fantasy elements, with stuff like giant bipedal cats. Maybe even a coming of age story! <span style="font-size: 50%;">(Is that even a genre?)<!--size--></span><br />
